   761→/**
   762→ * When used inside a [`$derived`](https://svelte.dev/docs/svelte/$derived) or [`$effect`](https://svelte.dev/docs/svelte/$effect),
   763→ * any state read inside `fn` will not be treated as a dependency.
   764→ *
   765→ * ```ts
   766→ * $effect(() => {
   767→ *   // this will run when `data` changes, but not when `time` changes
   768→ *   save(data, {
   769→ *     timestamp: untrack(() => time)
   770→ *   });
   771→ * });
